{"id":278975,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2013/02/维权网-上海浦东区委书记违法建别墅，民众请求/","date":"2013-02-13T08:01:17Z","modified":"2013-02-13T08:01:17Z","title":"维权网 | 上海浦东区委书记违法建别墅，民众请求查处至今无音讯（图）","content":"<p><div dir=\"ltr\"></p>\n<div></div>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" name='more'></a></p>\n<div><span>（维权网信息员张宁宁报道）上海市浦东新区区委副书记陆鸣不知用什么手段在崇明县向化镇阜康村获得一块集体土地，建一座豪华别墅，占地</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">4</span><span>亩许。该别墅位于阜康村</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">801</span><span>号。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>虽然陆鸣是浦东区委书记，但不是农村集体经济组织成员，按规定无权申请建房土地，所建别墅明显违法。当地村民对区委副书记陆鸣建豪华别墅的行为大为不满，纷纷向有关国家机关举报，但至今无音讯。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">2013</span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">1</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">13</span><span>日</span><span>，暴力拆迁受害人顾倩珏向崇明县向化镇规划土地局申请政府信息公开，请求公开该别墅建房批地手续等政府信息，但该土规局在法定期限内置之不理。顾倩珏对该土规局的行政不作为行为，表示将提起行政复议。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span><br /></span></div>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-ZnH_DF8p_9Q/URsCGa-yc-I/AAAAAAAAdC4/vgH68B3I1Us/s1600/000.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"220\" src=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-ZnH_DF8p_9Q/URsCGa-yc-I/AAAAAAAAdC4/vgH68B3I1Us/s320/000.jpg\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<div><span><br /></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span><br /></span></div>\n</div>\n</p>\n<p><small>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</small></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.us4.list-manage.com/subscribe/post?u=17daa75df533f6c6ff72e51ab&#038;id=b4fd4ae247\">\n<a href=\"http://eepurl.com/mstlf\">墙外新闻实时更新 欢迎订阅数字时代</a><br />\n <br /><input type=\"email\" value=\"\" name=\"EMAIL\" id=\"mce-EMAIL_in_post\" size=\"25\" style=\"display:block;\" placeholder=\"请输入您的邮件地址\" required><br />\n\t<input type=\"submit\" value=\"点击订阅\" name=\"subscribe\" style=\"height: 20px;\" id=\"in_post_subscribe\"><br />\n</form>\n","author":997,"categories":[18270,18269,20534],"tags":[16910]}